{"tid":2508098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有否繼續進口新疆貨？加拿大貿易部長拒答議員質詢","createTime":"2021-04-28T13:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T13:08:45.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b496fd55f8a11e8cf7be91f002190e37ff5262b","tid":2508098,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"加拿大國際貿易部長伍鳳儀（Mary Ng）在國會下議院國際貿易委員會（House of Commons&rsquo; international trade committee）上，被問加拿大有否禁止進口來自新疆的血汗商品時，迴避有關問題，被保守黨議員質疑當局執法不力。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大保守黨議員日前在國會上，向伍鳳儀提出質詢，查詢自1月實施新政策後，當局限制了多少由新疆進口的血汗商品，但伍鳳儀僅概括地講解政府實行了「全面措施」，但迴避有關問題，包括拒絕就聯邦政府執行措施的細節提供答案或數字。<br />\n<br />\n《多倫多星報》（Toronto Star）上月報導，約有400批來自新疆血汗工場的貨物，成功進口加拿大；加拿大《環球郵報》（Globe and Mail）另一篇報導亦指出，不少加拿大網店繼續出售進口自新疆的毛巾、衣物和其他產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210428/GPKPRZPGLZAZLCCR2XDA5OFI6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FGPKPRZPGLZAZLCCR2XDA5OFI6U%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzYvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=a271fd7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210428%2FGPKPRZPGLZAZLCCR2XDA5OFI6U%2F&h=3bfc3768\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210428/GPKPRZPGLZAZLCCR2XDA5OFI6U/</a>"},{"pid":"a1570089c76fb8f182daa39c4f4ada156651e958","tid":2508098,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"即係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}